    "description": "If you're a passionate Floor Manager with drive and ambition, Dulux Decorator Centre Ventures Solutions in Srinagar is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Dulux Decorator Centre Ventures Solutions:\nDulux Decorator Centre Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Dulux Decorator Centre Ventures Solutions!",
